   - .red[Unfavourable] self-interaction of \\(\sigma(\mathbf{s})\\)
   - .blue[Favourable] interaction of \\(\sigma(\mathbf{s})\\) and  \\(\varphi(\mathbf{s})\\)

2. Equilibrium values are energies
